---
// SocialProof.astro — Credibility line + testimonial cards
---

<section id="social-proof" class="section-pad">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <p class="credibility-line" data-reveal>
      5+ years of ML orchestration at <strong>JetBrains</strong>, <strong>Adeo</strong>, and the <strong>Bundeswehr</strong> — now applied to agents.
    </p>

    <div class="testimonial-grid">

      <div class="testimonial-card" data-reveal="scale-up" data-reveal-delay="1">
        <blockquote>
          <span class="open-quote">&ldquo;</span>
          <p>We were spending 40% of our agent development time on retry logic and state recovery. Kitaru replaced all of that with two decorators.</p>
          <footer class="testimonial-cite">— Engineering Lead, Series B AI startup</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card" data-reveal="scale-up" data-reveal-delay="2">
        <blockquote>
          <span class="open-quote">&ldquo;</span>
          <p>The replay capability alone saved us thousands in LLM costs during development. Being able to resume from a checkpoint instead of re-running everything is a game-changer.</p>
          <footer class="testimonial-cite">— ML Platform Engineer, Fortune 500</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .credibility-line {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .credibility-line strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .testimonial-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .testimonial-card blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .open-quote {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.3;
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .testimonial-cite {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
